    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but u keep saying it needs to be \"balanced\" with globalism and diversity. isn't that kind of just saying nationalism is only okay if it doesn't actually challenge the globalist status quo? like, if a country wants to put its own interests first above everything else, is that automatically considered \"extreme\" by u?",
